        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[举杠铃]#无氧运动过量可能诱发急性痛风#？是的。🙋🏻♂️有些无氧运动运动量过大，会造成体内乳酸堆积、尿酸排泄出现障碍。#为什么经常运动还会痛风#？大量...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举杠铃]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/bb/2022_Weightlifting_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%97%A0%E6%B0%A7%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%87%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E7%97%9B%E9%A3%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%97%A0%E6%B0%A7%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%87%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E7%97%9B%E9%A3%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#无氧运动过量可能诱发急性痛风#</span></a>？<br><br>是的。🙋🏻♂️<br><br>有些无氧运动运动量过大，会造成体内乳酸堆积、尿酸排泄出现障碍。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E7%97%9B%E9%A3%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E7%97%9B%E9%A3%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么经常运动还会痛风#</span></a>？大量运动后出汗多、尿量减少，若不及时补水，血尿酸可能骤升，诱发急性痛风关节炎。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>因此，医生建议，运动要适度，注意量力而行，即使不渴也要注意多喝水，维持代谢平衡。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnv4lqrdgsj20hc0hqdhh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 06:24:08 GMT</pubDate>
