        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[哈欠][困]#周末补觉2小时降低心脏病风险#】一般来说，大多数人每天需要拥有 7~9 小时的睡眠，才能保持身心健康。《2023年中国居民睡眠白皮书》显示，#调查显...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E8%A1%A5%E8%A7%892%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E8%A1%A5%E8%A7%892%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F%E7%97%85%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#周末补觉2小时降低心脏病风险#</span></a>】一般来说，大多数人每天需要拥有 7~9 小时的睡眠，才能保持身心健康。《2023年中国居民睡眠白皮书》显示，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%AC%A0%E4%BD%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%AC%A0%E4%BD%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#调查显示国人整体睡眠质量欠佳#</span></a>，平均在零点后入睡，夜间睡眠时长普遍偏短，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%97%B6%E9%95%BF6.75%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%97%B6%E9%95%BF6.75%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#国人平均睡眠时长6.75小时#</span></a>，平均清醒次数1.4次。<br><br>专家表示，如果你这一周都存在睡眠不足的情况，周末睡多1小时可以缓解疲劳，也能减少心血管疾病发生的风险 但最重要的还是要保证平时充足的睡眠，不能完全依靠周末补觉👇🏻（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4989356515983383" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hlqstrtej8j20u01hcju2.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nmPdm5AVlx08bGwPgapW01041200iHB30E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710782177&amp;ssig=1cuBq4k3Hm&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Fvx4Nd84lx08bGwP8NiM01041200aD1T0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710782177&amp;ssig=ZyIH%2B33lGL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nlgXK0vTlx08bGwPaLsA010412005Yiq0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710782177&amp;ssig=xI62a2k397&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4989356515983383" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
