            <description><![CDATA[【🫘<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%98%A5%E5%A4%A9%E5%90%83%E8%B1%86%E8%B5%9B%E8%BF%87%E5%90%83%E8%82%89%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%98%A5%E5%A4%A9%E5%90%83%E8%B1%86%E8%B5%9B%E8%BF%87%E5%90%83%E8%82%89%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#春天吃豆赛过吃肉#</span></a>】你喜欢吃豆子吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>？专家介绍，豆类蔬菜的蛋白质含量、矿物质元素和钙含量都比较高，对青少年骨骼发育、老年人钙流等情况，都有较好补钙效果。此外，豆类还具有高钾低钠的特点，对心脑血管疾病、需要控盐的人群好处多多👇🏻（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5012376127471643" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hns8kadk2qj21hc0u0gsb.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/gCNVvW0Slx08djE1Eekw01041200nqDR0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cx9YB1mmR49jS&amp;Expires=1710782162&amp;ssig=assOdgMEfG&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/gskeifnilx08djE1p7sY01041200bEsW0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cx9YB1mmR49jS&amp;Expires=1710782162&amp;ssig=NDzpdN3S%2Fp&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/F9PEPx5ilx08djE1eVgY010412007vgC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cx9YB1mmR49jS&amp;Expires=1710782162&amp;ssig=FdjQRirBJY&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5012376127471643" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
